<F P=102>   SK0306214294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1509 GMT 3 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0306214294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 3 (KCNA) -- Eleven political figures 
of foreign countries including the Politburo member of the C.C. 
[Central Committee], the Communist Party of Argentina, Jorge 
Alberto Craines, and the coordinator of the People's Party of 
Costa Rica, Eduardo Mora Valverde, in a joint statement 
published on May 22 held that for a durable peace and security 
