through DPRK-U.S. talks, and strongly urged the United States 
to get its forces out of South Korea. 
  It expressed the belief that the Korean people would surely 
achieve national reunification in accordance with the three 
principles of independence, peaceful reunification and great 
national unity laid down by President Kim Il-song. 

