Socialist Republic of Vietnam today decided to recognize the 
Republic of Macedonia. 
  The same day at the United Nations Headquarter in New York, 
Ambassador Le Van Bang, acting permanent representative of the 
SRV to the United Nations, and Dr. Denko Maleski, Macedonian 
