  [Text] Seoul, June 11 KYODO -- South Korean President Kim 
Yong-sam said Saturday [11 June] relatively lengthy U.N. 
Security Council discussions on sanctions against North Korea 
may help Pyongyang return to the negotiating table, Japanese 
