  [Text] Seoul, June 13 (YONHAP) -- President Kim Yong-sam 
said on Monday that South Korea would cope with the nuclear 
question with flexibility depending on the attitude of North 
Korea under the "grand principle that Pyongyang's nuclear 
development should be checked by all means." 
