<H3> <TI>   Arrest of Hanchongnyon Leaders in ROK Criticized </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Arrest of Hanchongnyon Leaders in ROK Criticized </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1206090094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0835 GMT 12 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1206090094 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Repressive Offensive Against Anti-war Forces" -- KCNA </F>
headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, June 12 (KCNA) -- The Kim Yong-sam 
fascist clique recently issued an order to the puppet police 
throughout South Korea to hurriedly arrest some 90 leading 
members of the South Korean Federation of General Student 
Councils (Hanchongnyon) including its chairman, alleging that 
"the disposition of Hanchongnyon benefiting the enemy was made 
clear." 
  In this regard, NODONG SINMUN today says this reckless 
repressive row kicked up by the Kim Yong-sam group is a 
premeditated fascist offensive to suppress and stifle 
Hanchongnyon, the vanguard of the anti-war, anti-nuke struggle 
for independence, democracy and reunification, and students. 
  The news analyst says: 
  The repressive offensive against Hanchongnyon was launched 
at 
a time when the Kim Yong-sam puppet clique was driving the 
situation to the worst phase, letting loose such bellicose 
utterances as "tough counteraction," "retaliatory punishment" 
and "sanctions" under the pretext of our "nuclear issue." 
  The Kim Yong-sam puppet clique are now serving the 
imperialists as a "shockbrigade" in their moves to take 
"sanctions" against us over the "nuclear suspicion." They are 
also getting overheated in arms buildup and nuclear war 
exercises in a bid to fulfil "the new operation plan 5027" they 
worked out with outside forces to invade the North. 
  The reality shows that the Kim Yong-sam group is going to 
make a military adventure against us in league with its master, 
the United States. 
  The South Korean puppets intend to suppress the pro- 
reunification, patriotic and democratic forces of South Korea 
including Hanchongnyon that they consider to be an obstacle to 
their criminal moves, thus stamping out the anti-U.S., anti-war, 
anti- nuke, anti-"government" forces at a stroke in South Korea. 
  The Kim Yong-sam group must be mindful that the further it 
is 
hell bent on the suppression of the people and war provocation 
moves, the earlier the day of its disgraceful destruction will 
come. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

